<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٣:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {كَلَّا لَئِنْ لَمْ يَنْتَهِ لَنَسْفَعًا بِالنَّاصِيَةِ <span class="c2">(١٥)</span> نَاصِيَةٍ كَاذِبَةٍ خَاطِئَةٍ <span class="c2">(١٦)</span> فَلْيَدْعُ نَادِيَهُ <span class="c2">(١٧)</span> سَنَدْعُ الزَّبَانِيَةَ <span class="c2">(١٨)</span>} <span class="c4">[العلق: ١٥ - ١٨]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{لَنَسْفَعَنْ}</span>: <span class="c1">" قَالَ: لَنَأْخُذَنْ , وَ <span class="c2">(لَنَسْفَعَنْ)</span> بِالنُّونِ , وَهِيَ الخَفِيفَةُ،<span class="c5"> سَفَعْتُ بِيَدِهِ:</span> أَخَذْتُ "</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{نَادِيَهُ}</span>: <span class="c2">«عَشِيرَتَهُ»</span>،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{الزَّبَانِيَةَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«المَلاَئِكَةَ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>